# 📓 Product Requirements Document (PRD): AE’s Notebook

## 📌 Product Name
**AE’s Notebook** – A productivity and planning tool built for B2B field Account Executives.

---

## 🎯 Purpose
AE’s Notebook helps enterprise sellers plan their week, track progress against quota, log customer meetings, and manage daily execution — all in one streamlined interface, accessible on both desktop and mobile.

---

## 👤 Target Users
- Enterprise and SMB B2B sales professionals  
- Field AEs managing a mix of prospecting, meetings, and quota attainment  
- RevOps leaders who want lightweight seller tools without bloated CRM systems  

---

## 🧠 Core Features

### 1. Notebook Structure
- Hierarchy: **Quarter → Week → Day**
- Sidebar navigation for:
  - Quarters (e.g., Q3 2025)
  - Weeks (e.g., Week 2: July 14–20)
  - Days (e.g., Mon, July 15)

---

### 2. Quota Overview
- Editable quota categories (e.g., "Hardware", "AI Deals")
- Fields for:
  - Quota Target by category
  - Attainment by category
- Auto-calculates percent to goal
- Collapsible UI:
  - Collapsed state hides totals and "+ Add Category" button
- Categories added via Enter or "+ Add Category" button

---

### 3. Weekly Target Accounts
- Add accounts via Enter or "+ Add Account" button
- Checkbox enabled
- Supports checkable bullet sub-tasks (via `Tab`)
- Copy button for exporting

---

### 4. Morning Tasks & To-Do List
- Daily reset (no carryover between days)
- Clean text box with checkable bullet per new line
- `Tab` creates an indented sub-task (also checkable)
- Rich text toolbar includes:
  - Indent
  - Undo/Redo
  - Checkmark bullet
  - Regular bullets
  - Numbered bullets
- Expands with page (no internal scrolling)
- No task counters or delete icons shown

---

### 5. Meeting Notes
- “Meeting Notes View” lists all notes across quarter
- Each note includes:
  - Title
  - Date
  - Category (default: “General Note”)
  - Body with rich text + image support
  - Reassignable to another day
- Sidebar remains visible in notes view
- Filter by category dropdown
- Notes auto-start with the text box open
- Copy button exports full note

---

## 🔐 Authentication

- **Supabase login**
  - Email & password
  - Forgot password via email token
- **Guest access**
  - No data persistence
- All data stored per user login (cloud-synced)

---

## 🧰 Platform & Tech Stack

| Component        | Tech/Service        |
|------------------|---------------------|
| Frontend         | React + Tailwind (Replit project) |
| Backend          | Supabase (auth & DB) |
| Hosting          | Netlify or Vercel   |
| State Management | Local + Supabase sync |
| Version Control  | GitHub              |

